<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Important: Data Security Notice</title>
    <style>
      body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f5; color: #18181b; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #6d28d9); padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; }
      .header h1 { color: #ffffff; font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 4px; font-weight: 700; }
      .header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size: 14px; margin: 0; }
      .body { padding: 32px 24px; }
      .notice-box { background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
      .notice-box p { margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #92400e; }
      h2 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #18181b; margin: 24px 0 8px; }
      p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #3f3f46; margin: 0 0 12px; }
      ul { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8; color: #3f3f46; padding-left: 20px; margin: 0 0 16px; }
      .cta { text-align: center; margin: 32px 0; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #7c3aed; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
      .footer { background: #f4f4f5; padding: 20px 24px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #71717a; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style='padding: 24px;'>
      <div class='container'>
        <div class='header'>
          <h1>Important: Security Notice</h1>
          <p>Vara Performance — Data Security Update</p>
        </div>
        <div class='body'>
          <div class='notice-box'>
            <p>We are writing to inform you of a security incident that may have affected your account.</p>
          </div>

          <h2>What Happened</h2>
          <p>
            On {{detectedAtFormatted}}, we identified a security incident involving our systems.
            We took immediate steps to contain the incident and secure your data.
          </p>

          <h2>Information Involved</h2>
          <p>The following categories of data may have been affected:</p>
          <ul>
            {{#each dataCategories}}
              <li>{{this}}</li>
            {{/each}}
          </ul>

          <h2>What We Are Doing</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>We have contained the incident and secured the affected systems.</li>
            <li>We have notified the relevant supervisory authority as required by law.</li>
            <li>We are conducting a full investigation to understand what happened.</li>
            <li>We are implementing additional security measures to prevent recurrence.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>What You Can Do</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Change your Vara Performance password as a precaution.</li>
            <li>Enable two-factor authentication if you have not already.</li>
            <li>Review your account activity for anything unusual.</li>
            <li>Be cautious of unsolicited emails or messages requesting your credentials.</li>
          </ul>

          <div class='cta'>
            <a href='{{frontendUrl}}/settings/security' class='btn'>Review Account Security</a>
          </div>

          <h2>Questions or Concerns</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about this notice or our response, please contact us at
            <a href='mailto:privacy@varaperformance.com'>privacy@varaperformance.com</a>.
            We take the security of your data very seriously and apologise for any inconvenience this may cause.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='footer'>
          <p>&copy; {{year}} Vara Performance. All rights reserved.</p>
          <p>You are receiving this email because you have an account with Vara Performance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
